      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 01:11:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产债务违约风险跃升至 2023 年 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/nissan-s-debt-default-risk-jumps-to-highest-since-march-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本汽车制造商日产汽车公司大幅下调盈利预期并表示将裁员 9,000 人之后，该公司债务违约风险指标跃升，这加剧了人们对该公司信贷状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/nissan-s-debt-default-risk-jumps-to-highest-since-march-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 00:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
